Extremely Loud & Incredibly Close(2011)
2012-02-26 06:36:06 GMT
Jonathan Safran Foer's novel of same name was critically panned but was commercially successful.The film adaption of the novel starring Tom hanks and Sandra Bullock tries to renew the ideas and emotions behind the novel.Releasing on Christmas day,the film is latest addition in the long list of films based on September 11 Attacks.The Plot follows a 10 year old boy named Oskar who loses his father in the 9 11 terrorist attacks.Oskar is Intelligent,pacifist,vegan and tambourine player.He finds a mysterious key left by his fathers.he sets up a journey around New York to find the lock that matches the key.Only thing he got as help is his grandfather and father's letters.
